Calculation of the cost of a repair between EUR 20,000 and EUR 30,000, including parts and workforce may take two or three hours.
On the contrary, with the support of the latest computer tools, it would be a question of minutes.
This is why almost 100% of experts use this type of systems.
The providers of services and solutions for disaster assessment and maintenance are dedicated to the collection of the information provided by the manufacturers, to then process and offer them to their customers in the form of a useful tool.
In Spain, Audatex, the North American Solera Group, is the leading company; 80% of estimates are made with its products.
Other companies in the field of evaluation and development of industry information are GtMotive and Eurotax.
