According to Eduardo Velázquez, Commercial Director of Audatex, the company in Spain with 63 manufacturers and importers, and each of them provides information in a different format.
In addition, the amount of data to be processed is constantly increasing, but more versions, variants and motorisations have only been launched over the past fifteen years.
When a new car runs on the market, these companies start working.
This is a very hard work, because you need to catalog each of the thousand pieces of the vehicle and register its price.
